msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/how-it-works/date-time.xml:43
msgid ""
"Time offsets in hours (+2, -10, etc.) have been replaced by time zones "
"(Europe/Berlin, America/New_York, etc.).  The conversion between time zones "
"is completely encapsulated within a DateTime object. If you want to convert "
"to another time zone, simply use the following code: <placeholder type="
"\"programlisting\" id=\"0\"/>"
