#. type: Content of: <section><section><para>
#: en/content/how-it-works/translations.xml:67
msgid ""
"The console command <filename>otrs.Console.pl Dev::Tools::"
"TranslationsUpdate</filename> is used to extract all translatable strings "
"from the source files. These will be collected and written into the "
