#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/how-to-extend-otrs/otrs-module-layers/gi-mapping.xml:312
msgid ""
"<literal>Empty</literal>: converts each data value into an empty string."
msgstr ""
"<literal>Empty</literal>: egy üres szövegre alakít át minden egyes "
