#: en/content/how-to-publish-otrs-extensions/package-porting/package-porting-5-to-6.xml:52
msgid ""
"Please note that the returned time values with the new <literal>Get()</"
"literal> function in the <literal>Kernel::System::DateTime</literal> module "
"are without leading zero instead of the old <literal>SystemTime2Date()</"
"literal> function in the <literal>Kernel::System::Time</literal> module.  In "
