#. type: Content of: <section><section><section><para>
#: en/content/how-to-publish-otrs-extensions/package-porting/package-porting-5-to-6.xml:131
msgid ""
"In OTRS 6, all admin modules should have a breadcrumb. The breadcrumb only "
"needs to be added on the .tt template file and should be placed right after "
"the h1 headline on top of the file. Additionally, the headline should "
"receive the class <code>InvisibleText</code> to make it only \"visible\" for "
"screen readers."
